Everyone has done something in their life that makes them feel like a piece of shit! You are learning. It’s ok. Just don’t let yourself tell yourself you are a piece of shit. You are your own biggest supporter. Tell yourself instead that hey, I did something that wasn’t the best thing but I am aware of it, I am learning from it and I want to do better. It’s called growth. Be kind to yourself
